    <p>
        <h1>Why put your eggs in one Basket?</h1>
    <p class="spacing">
        Here at EggBasket we want to ensure that your business is secured.
        With EggBasket you are able to implement structure into your business, projects, and security by
        having control of credential access. With the rise of cyber attacks, data breaches, social engineering
