        <h3>Credential Storing</h3>
        <p>EggBasket allows for users to safely share credentials. Rather then storing passwords in a sticky note, unsecured
        document, or out in the open in your work space.</p>
        <h3>Credential Sharing</h3>
        <p>EggBasket allows you to securily share credentials with employees.</p>
        <h3>Role Based Access</h3>
